To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Breakaway _breakaway;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_breakaway = Breakaway(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_breakaway.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "breakaway", _breakaway.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.breakaway = self.Breakaway(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.breakaway.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "breakaway", self.breakaway.Current.Value)
